      <title>孟加拉国下令关闭移动互联网以平息抗议活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/bangladesh-orders-mobile-internet-shutdown-to-quell-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为平息致命抗议活动，孟加拉国电信管理局下令三周内第二次关闭 4G 移动互联网服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/bangladesh-orders-mobile-internet-shutdown-to-quell-protests</guid>
