    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚总统称导致 13 人死亡的抗议活动是“政治事件”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/nigerian-president-calls-protests-that-killed-13-political</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚总统博拉·蒂努布表示，上周导致至少 13 人死亡的示威活动有政治目的，目的是破坏他的政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/nigerian-president-calls-protests-that-killed-13-political</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿联酋通过援助加沙和加强与以色列的关系展现外交影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/uae-shows-regional-diplomatic-sway-with-gaza-aid-ties-to-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿布扎比的影子已经来到了阿里什，这是一座位于西奈半岛北部的小城市，距离加沙约 50 公里。这个沿海城市曾经很少有外人来访，但现在却挤满了身穿工装裤和米色背心、印有阿联酋国旗的阿联酋志愿者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/uae-shows-regional-diplomatic-sway-with-gaza-aid-ties-to-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>骚乱持续，数十人被捕，恐将引发更多暴力事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-04/dozens-arrested-as-disorder-continues-with-fears-of-more-violence-to-come</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周六，英国各地出现骚乱，数十人被捕，并有警告称，未来几天可能还会有进一步的暴力事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-04/dozens-arrested-as-disorder-continues-with-fears-of-more-violence-to-come</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 04:25:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>疑似胡塞导弹袭击集装箱船 两周内首次遇袭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-04/suspected-missile-attack-by-yemen-s-houthi-rebels-hits-container-ship-in-first-attack-in-2-weeks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迪拜，阿拉伯联合酋长国（美联社）——当局周日称，一艘穿越亚丁湾的集装箱船疑似遭也门胡塞叛军导弹袭击，这可能是自以色列空袭以来该组织首次发动袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-04/suspected-missile-attack-by-yemen-s-houthi-rebels-hits-container-ship-in-first-attack-in-2-weeks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 01:54:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列准备应对伊朗袭击，美国将军访问中东</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/us-general-visits-middle-east-as-israel-braces-for-iran-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 Axios 报道，美国中央司令部将军迈克尔·库里拉于周六抵达中东，以色列正为应对伊朗可能发动的袭击做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/us-general-visits-middle-east-as-israel-braces-for-iran-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 01:38:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
